  BBUUGGSS

    There is no LISP support. Certain other features are missing, too.

    Auto-indent mode is not quite compatible with the real vvii(1). Among other
    things, 0^D and ^^D don't do what you might expect.

    Long lines are displayed differently. The real vvii(1) wraps long lines onto
    multiple rows of the screen, but eellvviiss(1) scrolls sideways.

